title: Breaking Down the Nets’ Big Win Over the 76ers | Real Ones
description:
Logan and Raja first talk about Kevin Garnett’s jersey retirement in Boston and the dry-aged beef between KG and Ray Allen (1:00). Then they dive into the Nets’ blowout win over the 76ers last week (9:00) and the Bucks’ loss to Golden State (30:00).
Hosts: Logan Murdock and Raja Bell
Producer: Sasha Ashall
Associate Producer: Mike Wargon
